snippet.title: OFFICIAL THE DIVISION 2 - WARLORDS OF NEW YORK - SEASON FOUR OVERVIEW
snippet.description:
This time it's personal! The Division has learned that Faye Lau, Division commander-turned rogue, is working together with four ex-Division operatives, recruited by Black Tusk, now under her command. 
 The Division must now track down Faye Lau, by neutralizing each of the rogue members of his cell and find out what exactly Faye Lau is plotting. 

Warlords of New York is available on PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One.

http://thedivisiongame.com/buy
